Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.13,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.34,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.14,0:00:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.42,0:01:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民卫星派来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五部钢弹的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是卫星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹躲藏起来避开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合军机动战士部队的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以OZ为攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开了各种作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ终于踏上历史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统帅特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以精锐的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行了消灭联合军的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派来地球的机动战士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.71,0:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的战斗令大地震动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.92,0:02:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有军人一定欢迎的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦平时沉默寡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他这样说一定没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要抗拒随感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是那样学习的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，那是我最后的大舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.71,0:02:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十三话\N[凯萨琳的眼泪]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯准备降下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预定降下路线附近\N有若干乱气流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯，一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降下准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10秒后射出，开始倒数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5，4，3，2，1，射出!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.91,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入对空雷达有效范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能捕捉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校!你没事吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到了，现在开始测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校，对空飞弹瞄准\N捕捉到托尔吉斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!发射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部机动战士正希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯又增加速度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!对空飞弹发射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这怪物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校…完全驾御了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好完美呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超级喷射器的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像和设计上不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，依照设计图的出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操作性能是会明显减低的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用技术补救那缺点是驾驶员的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消防班快灭火!快点…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是红坎沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲破敌人防卫线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在消灭前线基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓝天使了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别大意啊，亚雷克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是对我说的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先锋部队被消灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们有多少部!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,识别讯号确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的坎沙和艾亚利兹各一部!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!?只有两部?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动部队被消灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士毫无损伤!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然临时成军的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还对付不了OZ的机动战士吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的前线基地会马上解除武装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们准备好向OZ投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请求尽快做处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说投降?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不要搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是处决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停…停手!你们做什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲惨的过去遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受新时代的洗礼吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!你们的所为不是战争!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是屠杀!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该说过，这是处决!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你笑过头了，谬拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,维多利亚湖，好怀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.15,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵教官好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她永远都当我们是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让她看看我们增强的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚雷克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接通维多利亚基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是东北非洲索马利亚战线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第33独立战队的亚雷克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵特尉不在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵上级特尉现在去了莫斯科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫斯科?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和蕾蒂‧安特校一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，是特尉的单独行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.15,0:07:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要消灭旧联合的\N摩加迪要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此需要补给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望批准降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无实战经验的士兵是什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这基地何时起变成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧型机动战士的整备工场?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是诺茵特尉批准的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是杰克斯特校唆使她的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说起来，诺茵特尉今次出门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和杰克斯特校有关吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，但诺茵特尉是自愿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,部下杀手杰克斯\N那么值得尊敬吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也是服从杰克斯特校的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们服从的只是特列斯大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵特尉教导我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是为实现大人的理想而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，谬拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对这家伙说什么也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们增加士兵的人数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如我刚才所言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这基地没有实战经验的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.35,0:08:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫杰克斯‧马吉斯的优秀的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这些数据和回收了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01残骸的基本性能相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.33,0:08:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会知道驾驶员的战斗数值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,残骸的情形怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直是一堆废铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,01的自爆系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来完美地启动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员没有生还机会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?   什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个驾驶员不是人类吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是数据输入有错误…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么结果?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反应速度、筋肉力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有抵抗重力的能力都不寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说驾驶员是个少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是难以想像的数值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定在宇宙空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受了特殊的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我心理上的优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因此安全崩溃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我一直以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是机动战士性能上的差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那驾驶员或许能发挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.49,0:09:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部托尔吉斯原来的机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好的机体啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到特校有兴趣玩古董啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会认为它能在实战中使用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我已经使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西伯利亚的作战里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听说01自爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.34,0:10:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说的确在山克王国出击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时战死的驾驶员驾驶这古董
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想发挥他的技术也不能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们明天要进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧联合的摩加迪要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，只靠我们的机动战士部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗力不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想借这基地的士兵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，我用这部托尔吉斯出击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为你们的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.94,0:10:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校是部下!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,索马利亚战线是由你们负责的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.01,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我向杰克斯特校下达命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早0400时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用托尔吉斯出击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红坎沙，出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要远离我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为联合自豪的\N诺边塔炮不简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亚利兹部队出击准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬拉特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对雷达进行干扰没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.54,0:11:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们会被敌人发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说什么，杰克斯的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会比我们先被发现啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用杰克斯特校做饵吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了令诺边塔炮瞄准内陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是当然的战略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闪电伯爵的能耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达行动地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，放下托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红坎沙来电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说祝你奋勇作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不祝我，我也会奋勇作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯射出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现敌机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从内陆上空一直飞来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.96,0:12:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连这么偏僻的地方\N也不放过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用诺边塔炮!别让敌人接近!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉到目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射方位角度良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺边塔炮发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HP弹的弹幕确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高热源体从6时方向接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向戒备中的里欧部队降下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人没被击落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超级喷射器的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?\N为何不发射诺边塔炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.58,0:13:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士太快\N不能捕捉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌人由海面入侵了\N怎么办? 司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到这个要塞会这么脆弱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士有通讯进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在映出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.15,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是第33独立战队所属的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你失去了最大的防御网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进一步的战斗是无意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你马上解除武装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是渴望和平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已故诺边塔大人的意愿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的机动战士部队被消灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第5区也被毁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了…我投降!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们做什么!?\N亚雷克斯!谬拉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻击\N对方已经同意投降!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越权也要有限度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望之后你把他们交由我们处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这班人是旧联合有待处决的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处决!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这班人是阻挡时代洪流的蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我们要清除淤塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.24,0:15:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，这是肃清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肃清肃清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶…!OZ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然用到…\N这么卑鄙的手段…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令部中弹!继续攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们那样也算OZ的士兵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么残暴…不，卑鄙的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知羞耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬拉队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校叫我停止攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧…OZ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢叛变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.76,0:16:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你的错!你的错令他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来轻视了这部机体的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着送你去你想去的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟…糟了!他呢!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的技术了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但作为诺茵的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的思想太差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.62,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴!\N不要说诺茵教官的名字!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个时代令他疯了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.36,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别太威风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.19,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，这班人没资格拥有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喷射器的状态果然很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亚雷克斯和谬拉那件事的报告书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那份报告书送去给诺茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给诺茵特尉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[只能教导技术]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫她反省那错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争是无情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争真是无情的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在修复敌人的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.61,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他们一样，我没资格做军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装有20部穿梭机燃料的运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.39,0:18:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ宇宙军的准备终于开始了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，压轴表演开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本马戏团的新星
